(66, -1, 'skimlinks_global_tos_note', 'cpglobal', '<small style="display: block; margin: 8px 0;"><strong>Note:</strong>\r\n						By activating your Skimlinks account, you are agreeing to abide by the Skimlinks Terms of Service. This contract will be between you and Skimlinks. You will be able to\r\n						track your site''s Skimlinks revenue by logging into your Skimlinks account, and revenues generated by the use of Skimlinks will be issued to the associated Skimlinks account.\r\n						The details you provide here will be sent to Skimlinks and your account immediately activated.\r\n						<br /><br />Please add support@skimlinks.com to your email safe list as all email contact\r\n						from Skimlinks, including your account information and login, will come from this address.</small>', 'skimlinks', 'Skimlinks', 1297120015, '3.0'),
