(104, -1, 'skimwords_options_description', 'cpoption', 'SkimWords will automatically convert product references in posts into shopping links. Since SkimWords adds links where there weren''t any before, it is visible to your end users. However, it is well-targeted and never adds too many links to the page. For the best revenue opportunity is is recommended to be enabled for <b>all</b> usergroups and forums.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou may hide SkimWords features from visitors belonging to specific usergroups, or disable it for entire forums.\r\nNote that if a user belongs to <i>any</i> usergroup that has SkimWords disabled, this will disable SkimWords for them regardless of\r\ntheir membership of any groups that may have SkimWords enabled.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<b>Note</b>: You must ensure SkimWords is enabled in your publisher admin settings page.', 'skimlinks', 'Skimlinks', 1289751845, '2.3.1'),
