(594, -1, 'bbcode_add_edit_buttonimage_text', 'cphelptext', 'If you would like this BB code to appear as a clickable button on the message editor toolbar, enter the URL of an image 16 x 16 pixels in size that will act as the button to insert this BB code.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1303396069, '4.1.4 Beta 1'),
