(2172, -1, 'options_options_showsimilarthreads_text', 'cphelptext', 'This setting displays the similar thread box.  The <a href="options.php?do=options&amp;dogroup=search" target="_blank">Automatic Similar Thread Search</a> option does the actual work to find similar threads.  Disable both options if you don''t want this feature.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, ''),
