(2178, -1, 'options_options_threadedmode_text', 'cphelptext', 'Threaded mode shows a tree of links to individual posts within the thread.  The tree shows the threading of the posts by indenting reply posts under the post they are in reply to.  Only one post is viewable at a time.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1205942492, '3.7.0 Release Candidate 1'),
