(2222, -1, 'options_options_archive_threadtype_text', 'cphelptext', 'Disabling this option will cause the thread links in the archive to link to the actual threads on the main forum (dynamic URLs and all).  For example, instead of:<br /><br />\r\n\r\n<i>http://www.yoursite.com/forum/archive/index.php/t-1.html</i><br /><br />\r\n\r\n...you will get:<br /><br />\r\n\r\n<i>http://www.yoursite.com/forum/showthread.php?t=1</i>', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, ''),
