(2356, -1, 'prefix_addset_editset_forumids_text', 'cphelptext', 'Prefix sets must be attached to forums before they can be used. Select the forum or forums this prefix set will be available in using this field. Once you do this, when a user creates a new thread in a selected forum, he or she will be able to select a prefix from this set.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1190048861, '3.7.0 Beta 1'),
