(2358, -1, 'prefix_addset_editset_displayorder_text', 'cphelptext', 'The sorting order for sets. Sets with lower values will be shown before sets with higher values.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNote that the display order setting for individual prefixes only controls their order within the set.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1190047556, '3.7.0 Beta 1'),
