(2370, -1, 'profilefield_add_edit_description_text', 'cphelptext', 'This is the description of the field as shown to your users. You should describe here what the field is intended for, and if it is required field or not, and/or if it is private from other users or not.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, ''),
