(2372, -1, 'profilefield_add_edit_profilefieldcategoryid_text', 'cphelptext', 'It is possible to group custom user profile fields into categories so that they can be logically grouped. The primary purpose of doing this is to allow different categories to be shown in different tabs or blocks on a user''s profile page (in addition to being shown in the ''About Me'' tab).<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href="help.php?do=answer&amp;page=profilefield&amp;pageaction=editcat">For further information, see the help entry for the profile field category manager.</a>', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1205937526, '3.7.0 Release Candidate 1'),
(2373, -1, 'profilefield_add_edit_profilefieldcategoryid_title', 'cphelptext', 'Profile Field Category', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1205937422, '3.7.0 Release Candidate 1'),
(2374, -1, 'profilefield_add_edit_data_text', 'cphelptext', '<b>Select Fields</b><br />\r\nIn this box, put each value that should appear as an option. Make sure to press Enter after each option or it will not work correctly!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<b>Radio Fields</b><br />\r\nIn this box, put each value that should appear as a radio button. Make sure to press Enter after each option or it will not work correctly!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<b>Checkbox Fields</b><br />\r\nIn this box, put each value that should appear as a checkbox. Make sure to press Enter after each option or it will not work correctly!', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, ''),
