(2410, -1, 'profilefield_editcat_text', 'cphelptext', 'It is possible to group custom user profile fields into categories so that they can be logically grouped. The primary purpose of doing this is to allow different categories to be shown in different tabs or blocks on a user''s profile page (in addition to being shown in the ''About Me'' tab).', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1205936925, '3.7.0 Release Candidate 1'),
