(2440, -1, 'ranks_add_edit_ranklevel_text', 'cphelptext', 'This is the number of times that this rank image or text will be repeated when it is displayed next to a user''s name in their posts.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nFor example, if you specify a rank text of "Captain" and this setting is set to 2, then the user''s rank will be shown as "CaptainCaptain".', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, ''),
