(2452, -1, 'ranks_add_edit_display_text', 'cphelptext', '<strong>Always</strong>: This rank will always be displayed if a member has this rank''s usergroup as their primary or one of their secondary groups.<br /><br />\r\n<strong>If Displaygroup = This Group</strong>: This rank will only be displayed if a member''s displaygroup is equal to this rank''s usergroup.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, ''),
