(2502, -1, 'rssposter_edit_url_text', 'cphelptext', 'This box should contain the complete URL of the feed to be read.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor example: <code>http://www.vbulletin.com/forum/external.php?type=RSS2&amp;forumids=1</code>', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1149677544, '3.6.0 Beta 1'),
