(2504, -1, 'rssposter_edit_ttl_text', 'cphelptext', 'While the RSS Poster scheduled task runs every ten minutes, you can limit the frequency at which this feed is checked.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1149677740, '3.6.0 Beta 1'),
