(2552, -1, 'socialgroups_editcategory_title_text', 'cphelptext', 'This is the title of the Group Category.  This will be displayed in the breadcrumb when viewing a group or filtering by categories.  It will also be displayed in the category cloud in the Group overview page.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1260378100, '4.0.0 Release Candidate 2'),
