(2698, -1, 'template_add_edit_template_text', 'cphelptext', '<p>This is where you actually edit the HTML. Any valid HTML is allowed here. To learn how to use HTML please visit www.w3c.org.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>vBulletin also provides some specialized tags that can be used here. These include the &lt;phrase&gt; tag and the &lt;if&gt; tag.  Please see the General Topic named "About vBulletin Styles" by clicking on the help image in a title bar.</p>', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, ''),
