(3282, -1, 'usergroup_add_edit_pmquota_text', 'cphelptext', 'This permission determines how many private messages members of this group can have in their private message folders.  If a user reaches this limit then they will need to delete some PMs before they can receive anymore.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nPrivate Messaging must be enabled in your <a href="options.php?dogroup=pm&amp;do=options" target="_blank">vBulletin options</a> for this permission to have any effect.  Additionally, there are other private message settings on that page in your vBulletin options.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, ''),
