(3314, -1, 'usergroup_add_edit_canmanageownusernotes_text', 'cphelptext', 'To be able to <i>manage</i> user notes means to be able to edit and delete notes.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nUser notes can be managed through the <i>[View]</i> page for notes.  That page is opened by clicking the <i>User Notes: [View]</i> link when viewing a user''s profile page on the frontend.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1205942890, '3.7.0 Release Candidate 1'),
