(3316, -1, 'usergroup_add_edit_canpostownusernotes_text', 'cphelptext', 'A new user note can be posted by first clicking the <i>User Notes: [View]</i> link when viewing a user''s profile page on the frontend and then clicking the <i>Post New User Note</i> link.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, ''),
