(12973, -1, 'setting_attachmentviewslive_desc', 'vbsettings', 'Option to update attachment views immediately, or once an hour. If you have a large number of inline graphic attachments, you will probably want to disable immediate updates, since they are quite server intensive.', 'vbulletin', '', 0, ''),
